title: Chennai girl Rochelle confirms relationship
text:
Model and anchor Rochelle Maria Rao, who was the winner of the Femina Miss India International 2012 will be participating in controversial reality show 'Bigg Boss 9'. With the show, hosted by Salman Khan set to go on air from today, the sizzling model, who was the sexy host of Extraaa Innings during the sixth edition of IPL has declared her relationship with VJ Keith Sequeira, who will also be contesting in the show. Interestingly, Rochelle got paired up with Prince Narula and Keith Sequira has been paired with Mandana Karimi.
VJ Keith Sequeira and Rochelle Maria Rao were rumoured to be in a relationship for sometime, but the couple took to Facebook to confirm the reports. The makers of the reality show, hosted by Salman Khan, have roped in couples and ex-couples among others for the ninth season of the reality show.
Rochelle posted about the show and Keith, "Looking at all my loved one's updates right now and thinking how much I'm gonna miss social media from tomorrow! Also just how much I'm gonna miss everyone and life in the real world... However the beauty queen in me can't help getting excited and revved up for yet another competition!! This time I get to go in hand in hand with the one I love and that makes it all the better. Keith Sequeira. I ask all my friends and family to pls Pray for Us! Send us all your love and positive vibes. Forgive us in advance for the times we might lose ourselves in there and most of all believe in the best for us and remember "reality shows" are still just "shows" ‪#‎LoveandLight."
